Title: An Act Changing the Name of the South Elementary School in the City of San Carlos to Congressman Vicente Gustilo, Sr. Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 835
An Act Changing the Name of the South Elementary School in the City of San Carlos to Congressman Vicente Gustilo, Sr. Memorial School
Section 1. The name of the South Elementary School in the City of San Carlos, Negros Occidental, is changed to Congressman Vicente Gustilo, Sr. Memorial School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
